&lt;h2&gt;Welcome to English 202C, Technical Communication&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This advanced course in writing familiarizes students with the discourse practices prized in their disciplinary and institutional communities, and helps them to manage those practices effectively in their own written work. In this way the course teaches those writing strategies and tactics that scientists, engineers, and others will need in order to write successfully on the job.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The activities you will complete this week are designed to familiarize you with both your classmates and the course. Each week in the course centers on two discussion forums. The first will take place in the early part of the week (Monday-Thursday), and the second will take place in the latter part  (Thursday-Sunday). This routine will be repeated throughout the semester.&lt;/p&gt;
